        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Direktno promatranje pokretljivosti pod mikroskopom.</p>
        <a href="/mikroskopsko-ispitivanje/" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors duration-300">
          Pročitaj više →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Polučvrsti mediji -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Polučvrsti mediji</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Ispitivanje pokretljivosti na polučvrstim medijima.</p>
        <a href="/polucvrsti-mediji/" class="text-green-600 font-semibold hover:text-green-800 transition-colors duration-300">
          Pročitaj više →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Interpretacija rezultata -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Interpretacija rezultata</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Kako pravilno interpretirati rezultate testova pokretljivosti.</p>
        <a href="/interpretacija-rezultata/" class="text-purple-600 font-semibold hover:text-purple-800 transition-colors duration-300">
          Pročitaj više →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Praktične vježbe -->
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Praktične vježbe</h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Vježba 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-yellow-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
